    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Holotype of Phyllodytes iuna sp. nov. (MZUESC 18950). (A) Dorsal view of head; (B) Lateral view of head (right side); (C) Palmar view of left hand; (D) Plantar view of left foot. Scale bar = 3 mm" ;
